---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Sharing AR Experience Between HMD and Non-HMD Users - Research Project";
const metaDescription = "Research on investigating methods to bridge the gap between HMD and non-HMD users in AR environments.";

// 项目信息
const project = {
    title: "Sharing AR Experience Between HMD and Non-HMD Users",
    featuredImage: "/images/sharing-ar-experience-page/featured-image.png",
    description: "This research explores methods to create shared augmented reality experiences between users wearing head-mounted displays (HMD) and those without HMDs, enabling collaborative interactions across different AR access methods.",
    dateStart: "2018-05",
    dateEnd: "2019-06",
    funding: "",
    collaborators: [
        {
            name: "Shihui Xu",
            role: "Lead Author & Graduate Student",
            affiliation: "Waseda University",
            email: "shxu@toki.waseda.jp",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        },
        {
            name: "Bo Yang",
            role: "Graduate Student",
            affiliation: "Waseda University",
            email: "kuroiiimizu@akane.waseda.jp",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        },
        {
            name: "Boyang Liu",
            role: "Graduate Student",
            affiliation: "Waseda University",
            email: "waseda-liuboyang@moegi.waseda.jp",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        },
        {
            name: "Kelvin Cheng",
            role: "Researcher",
            affiliation: "Rakuten Institute of Technology",
            email: "kelvin.cheng@rakuten.com",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        },
        {
            name: "Soh Masuko",
            role: "Researcher",
            affiliation: "Rakuten Institute of Technology",
            email: "so.masuko@rakuten.com",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        },
        {
            name: "Jiro Tanaka",
            role: "Supervisor",
            affiliation: "Waseda University",
            email: "jiro@aoni.waseda.jp",
            avatar: "/avatars/Avatar.svg"
        }
    ],
    relatedPublications: [
        {
            title: "Sharing Augmented Reality Experience Between HMD and Non-HMD User",
            venue: "Human Interface and the Management of Information. Information in Intelligent Systems: Thematic Area, HIMI 2019",
            authors: "Shihui Xu, Bo Yang, Boyang Liu, Kelvin Cheng, Soh Masuko, and Jiro Tanaka",
            link: "/publications#himi2019"
        }
    ]
};
---

<MainLayout title={title} metaDescription={metaDescription}>
    <div class="container project-container">
        <div class="project-header">
            <h1 class="project-title">{project.title}</h1>
            <div class="project-meta">
                <span class="project-date">{project.dateStart} – {project.dateEnd}</span>
                <span class="project-funding">{project.funding}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-featured-image">
            <img src={project.featuredImage} alt={project.title}>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-content">
            <div class="project-main">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>This research addresses a critical gap in current augmented reality (AR) systems, which primarily focus on enhancing experiences for head-mounted display (HMD) users while excluding bystanders without HMDs. We propose an innovative solution that enables the sharing of AR experiences between HMD and non-HMD users through smartphone visualization and synchronization of virtual objects.</p>
                
                <p>Our system allows non-HMD users to directly view and interact with virtual objects on their smartphones, creating a more inclusive AR experience. This approach is particularly valuable in e-commerce contexts, where it enables both HMD users to interact with virtual products for better real product understanding, while non-HMD users can have similar AR experiences through their smartphones.</p>
                
                <h2>Research Objectives</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enable HMD users to share augmented reality information with non-HMD users</li>
                    <li>Allow non-HMD users to interact with the same virtual objects as HMD users</li>
                    <li>Create a synchronized viewing experience between HMD and smartphone displays</li>
                    <li>Facilitate social media sharing of AR experiences through video rendering</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h2>Methodology</h2>
                <p>Our research employs a comprehensive approach:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>User studies with mixed groups of HMD and non-HMD users</li>
                    <li>Development of shared interaction techniques</li>
                    <li>Prototype testing and iterative refinement</li>
                    <li>Evaluation of collaboration effectiveness</li>
                </ol>
                
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Smartphone-based visualization of virtual objects for non-HMD users</li>
                    <li>Real-time synchronization of HMD user's view to smartphone displays</li>
                    <li>Direct interaction capabilities for non-HMD users through smartphones</li>
                    <li>Social media sharing functionality for AR experiences</li>
                    <li>Enhanced e-commerce experience through virtual product interaction</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h2>Technical Implementation</h2>
                <p>The system incorporates several key technologies:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>See-through type AR head-mounted displays for immersive experiences</li>
                    <li>Smartphone-based AR visualization and interaction</li>
                    <li>Real-time view synchronization between HMD and smartphone</li>
                    <li>Video rendering capabilities for social media sharing</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Demo Video</h2>
                <div class="video-container">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VNsWWdrqrKA"
                        title="Sharing AR Experience Demo"
                        frameborder="0"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                        allowfullscreen>
                    </iframe>
                </div>
                
                <h2>Future Directions</h2>
                <p>Future work will focus on:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enhanced cross-platform interaction methods</li>
                    <li>Improved spatial awareness sharing</li>
                    <li>Advanced collaboration features</li>
                    <li>Integration with existing AR platforms</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="project-sidebar">
                <div class="sidebar-section">
                    <h3 class="sidebar-title">Team Members</h3>
                    <div class="team-members">
                        {project.collaborators.map(member => (
                            <div class="team-member">
                                <img src={member.avatar} alt={member.name} class="member-avatar">
                                <div class="member-info">
                                    <div class="member-name">{member.name}</div>
                                    <div class="member-role">{member.role}, {member.affiliation}</div>
                                    <div class="member-email">{member.email}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="sidebar-section">
                    <h3 class="sidebar-title">Related Publications</h3>
                    <ul class="related-publications">
                        {project.relatedPublications.map(pub => (
                            <li>
                                <a href={pub.link}>{pub.title}</a>
                                <span class="publication-venue">{pub.venue}</span>
                            </li>
                        ))}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .project-container {
        padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
    }
    
    .project-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .project-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        color: var(--color-text);
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .project-title:after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 25%;
        width: 50%;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
    }
    
    .project-meta {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
    }
    
    .project-featured-image {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 5px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }
    
    .project-featured-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: block;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
    
    .project-video {
        margin: 2.5rem 0;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .project-video h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .video-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 宽高比 */
        height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 1.5rem auto;
    }
    
    .video-container iframe {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: none;
    }
    
    .project-content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
    }
    
    .project-main h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .project-main h2:first-child {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    .project-main p, 
    .project-main ul, 
    .project-main ol {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .project-main ul, 
    .project-main ol {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .project-main li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .project-main strong {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .project-sidebar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 6rem;
        align-self: start;
    }
    
    .sidebar-section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        background-color: var(--color-background);
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .sidebar-title {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        position: relative;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .sidebar-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 30px;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
    }
    
    .team-members {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .team-member {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .member-avatar {
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 2px solid var(--color-primary-light);
    }
    
    .member-info {
        flex-grow: 1;
    }
    
    .member-name {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .member-role {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
    }
    
    .member-email {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
    
    .related-publications li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .related-publications a {
        display: block;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .related-publications a:hover {
        color: var(--color-accent);
    }
    
    .publication-venue {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        font-style: italic;
    }
    
    .publication-authors {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }
    
    .cta-section {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .cta-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .cta-text {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 2px;
        font-weight: 400;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: var(--color-accent);
        color: white;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .project-content {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        
        .project-sidebar {
            position: static;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .video-container {
            max-width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
        }
    }
</style> 